A Look at Heloderma Morphometrics

Who Will Win?

This webpage highlights some preliminary analysis done on Gila monster morphometrics comparing body proportions of males and females of the species. This comparison aims to investigate different facets of sexual selection that may exist in this species.

A male and a female Gila monster side by side

A Brief Summary of the Data Collected

This data has a total of 127 measured specimens. The average SVL is 261.03 millimeters. SVLs range from 120 to 389 millimeters

Looking at the Belly of the Beast
